query:
SELECT
    AVG(fuel_consumption) as fuel
FROM
    trips_detailed t
WHERE
    t.start_timestamp >= $1
    AND t.stop_timestamp <= $2
    AND (
        $3::INT IS NULL
        OR t.fiskeridir_length_group_id = $3
    )
    AND (
        $4::INT[] IS NULL
        OR t.haul_gear_group_ids && $4
    )
